data.description: NEW PRICE this could mean new home for you right before the holidays! Still time to close by end of the year! Are you on the search for 2023 SPACIOUS home in Mustang? Here it is! It features a BEAUTIFUL 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, over 2300 sq ft and one of the BIGGEST lots I have personally seen for a home in this price range for new construction. BUILDER TRANSFERRABLE WARRANTY. Plenty of recessed lighting. The kitchen is on the far right wall of first floor, creating an open space concept for dining and living room. Kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, plenty of cabinet storage space, walk-in pantry. Plus a nice sized island, making it easier to cook and watch television if desired. Add convenience as all 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and laundry room located in the second floor. Master bedroom is spacious plus his & hers walk-in closets. The other 3 bedrooms are nicely sized. Security system is owned. The backyard has a big lot, over 8000 land sq ft. Equipped with SPRINKLER SYSTEM. Conveniently located, close to schools, parks, shopping centers, restaurants & highways. Mustang has had a LOT of development the last few years, don’t miss the opportunity to be a part of this expansion while you enjoy living in a beautiful turn-key home!
